        "subject": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in lfs_find()",
        "message": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in lfs_find()\n\nError and warning messages in lfs_find() are updated to a standard\nformat.  Messages are prefixed with the name of the utility and the\ncommand that caused the error.  User-provided values are delimited\nwith single quotes.\n\nMessages that duplicate information provided by the llapi functions\nhave been removed.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Steve Guminski <stephenx.guminski@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I06f3669c800d246a7f3318efaeda0245e70c3b26\n"
